wiki.summary: In “Spin Bout U,” sampled by the slow, R&B-influenced lyrics from B.G.O.T.I.’s 1995, “Give Me Your Lov-N,” 21 Savage begins his verse in a slow tone. Drake’s chorus contrasts 21’s verse as well as his own. In the song, both artists rap about taking care of a woman while boasting about their money and worth compared to other men who are interested in the same female. “Spin Bout U” debuted at #5 on the Billboard Hot 100 during the chart week ending of November 19, 2022. Read more on Last.fm.
